title: Daily Review with Clay and Buck - Oct 28 2022

description:
Desperate Biden straight-up lies about gas prices and inflation. General Don Bolduc on why he could be the Senate difference maker if victorious in New Hampshire. Tudor Dixon: Michigan children lost 30 years of progress because of Whitmer’s covid policies. Doug Mastriano on his plan to defy the odds to become Governor of Pennsylvania.
